SVGAnimatedPreserveAspectRatio.summary: The SVGAnimatedPreserveAspectRatio interface represents attributes of type which can be animated.

SVGAnimatedPreserveAspectRatioAnimVal.summary: The animVal read-only property of the interface represents the value of the {{SVGAttr("preserveAspectRatio")}} attribute of an SVG element after any animations or transformations are applied.

SVGAnimatedPreserveAspectRatioBaseVal.summary: The baseVal read-only property of the interface represents the base (non-animated) value of the {{SVGAttr("preserveAspectRatio")}} attribute of an SVG element.
